       <div class="term-card"><div class="row1"><span class="val">CESS · CS</span></div><p>Sustainment planning.</p></div>
-      <div class="term-card"><div class="row1"><span class="val">AOTO · OTO</span></div><p>Acquisition / test-to-operations transition.</p></div>
-      <div class="term-card"><div class="row1"><span class="val">ADO · D4</span></div><p>Army Data Office / ASB4 — data integration and cloud, AI, and digitalisation front-end planning.</p></div>
+      <div class="term-card"><div class="row1"><span class="val">AOTO · AO</span></div><p>Acquisition / test-to-operations transition.</p></div>
